This might sound like:
‚ÄúI‚Äôm sure he / she only has your best interests at heart‚Äù
‚ÄúWhat did you do to make them feel like that?‚Äù
‚Äúhe / she only yelled at you because you made him / her so angry with what you did‚Äù
