This might sound like:
‚ÄúIf you loved me‚Ä¶‚Äù
‚ÄúEvery decent person would‚Ä¶‚Äù or ‚ÄúYou should be grateful you have me‚Ä¶‚Äù ‚ÄúDo you think anyone else would want you?‚Äù
‚ÄúYou would be nothing without me‚Äù,
