This might sound like: ‚ÄúWhat will people say if you leave? You made your decision and you have to stop being so ungrateful.‚Äù
What happens? Normalisation refers to social processes through which ideas and actions are seen as culturally ‚Äúnormal‚Äù in everyday life. Manipulative people take full advantage of this and use it against you.
