This may sound like: ‚ÄúYou are so lazy!‚Äù / ‚ÄúYou forget to do this every time!‚Äù / ‚ÄúEveryone knows that you‚Äôre bad.‚Äù
What happens? These generalise a person‚Äôs character or behaviour in a negative way. They often involve the use of words such as ‚Äúalways,‚Äù‚Äúnever,‚Äù‚Äúagain,‚Äù‚Äúso,‚Äù‚Äúevery time,‚Äù‚Äúsuch as,‚Äù and ‚Äúeveryone.‚Äù
